sidebar_label: Liveness check with Face Verification

:::note
Prerequisite : Acquire requestID from mykad recognition response
:::
Description: Please obtain the Liveness JS web sdk and sample code from Revenue Monster

### Step 1. Navigate to API Key Page
Generate an API Key in the API Key page.
![image](/img/ekyc/liveness-sdk-step-1.jpg)

### Step 2. Generate API Key
Enter a name and select ekyc.liveness as a scope. Click confirm. An API Key should be
generated, store it in your application environment.
![image](/img/ekyc/liveness-sdk-step-2.jpg)

### Step 3.Download the SDK.
Acquire the Liveness Web SDK from Revenue Monster.

### Step 4. SDK Integration (Basic example)
Embedding the SDK into your web project is simple. Only a few parameters are required, they
are as follows

a. apiKey – API Key generated from step 2<br/>
b. requestId – Can be obtained from the MyKad Recognition response payload<br/>
c. autoInit – Optional boolean value. Specifying it to false allows you to have a
customization splash screen. Default to true.

A simple HTML example below should be sufficient to get the liveness app started.
![image](/img/ekyc/liveness-sdk-code.jpg)


**Method :** <span style={{ color: "orange", fontWeight: "bold" }}>POST</span><br/>

URL: `https://ekyc.revenuemonster.my/`<br/>

Sandbox URL: `https://sb-ekyc.revenuemonster.my/`

### Request Parameters

| Parameter             | Type   | Description                                | Example                    |
| --------------------- | ------ | ------------------------------------------ | -------------------------- |
| `mykad_request_id`    | String | Request ID from mykad recognition response | "62201d48a694817dede84b35" |
| `query_image_content` | String | Face image (Base64 image string)           | ""                         |

### Response Parameters

:::note

- Current type in <b>Status</b> will be :-

  - "SUCCESS" <br/>
  - "FACE_ENGINE_CONNECTION_ERROR" <br/>
  - "INCOMPLETE" <br/>
  - "FACE_ENGINE_TIMEOUT" <br/>

- Current type in <b>Action</b> will be :-
  - "NONE_REQUIRED"<br/>
  - "ATTENTION_REQUIRED"<br/>
  - "INCONCLUSIVE"<br/>
  - "RESOLVED"<br/>

:::

| Parameter      | Type     | Description                           | Example                      |
| -------------- | -------- | ------------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| `id`           | String   | Table ID                              | "60f79b737b03abf23ad65206"   |
| `ekycId`       | String   | EKYC ID                               | "62201e0b239b18052126e28b"   |
| `action`       | String   | Action Required                       | NONE_REQUIRED                |
| `status`       | String   | Verfication Status                    | SUCCESS                      |
| `isSamePerson` | Boolean  | Visualization for result image        | true                         |
| `similarity`   | Int      | Percentage of similarity of two faces | 99                           |
| `updatedAt`    | DateTime | Last update date time                 | "2021-07-21T15:07:43.266243" |

> Example Response

```json

  "item": {
    "id": "62201e0a239b18052126e28a",

  }
```
